Text.string: Skag dogs! You don't know what's in 'em, but you KNOW you want 'em. At least, that USED to be true. Now people want REAL skag meat and FANCY toppings. Ugh, there's some cacti fruits that will appease the masses. Gives a spicy tang to my dogs—and covers the aftertaste. Harvest some of those succulent succulents and you get paid.
Right, you're gonna need a special gun to harvest those succulents. I call it the “Big Succ”. 'Cause it harvests succulents! Whatever, I'm a chef. Not a... namer of things.
Ooh! There's always an alpha. Succ it up for me!
Wow, you killed a succulent alpha skag with the Big Succ? Good succ'ing! You might just be chef material after all!
“Being a chef is my dream!” said no one ever.
My eight hands would crush the culinary world. But I'm not interested.
I have no interest in cooking flesh. A chef's life is not for me.
I've had some of the dirtiest jobs in the galaxy... but not a chef.
Well, being a chef ain't for everybody. Now go grab that skag meat.
It looks like somebody's been poaching my succulents, which means in chef code that THEY MUST DIE! Gotta be the bandit chef Mincemeat! Go kill him.

Ohhh, it's all coming together. Soon, I'll make my spatula-wielding rival PAY for what he's done. But first, we'll make my NEW rival MINCEMEAT pay! Listen, a chef's life is half-revenge killings. It's a thing.
All right, watch out for Mincemeat's skags, Trufflemunch and Buttmunch. They will munch anything... including you.
The chef is dead! The chef is dead!||—Whoa. Just got déjà vu.
I made mincemeat of Mincemeat. Nailed it!
I have prepared Chef Mincemeat for his final meal.
That's twelve chefs I've killed. One more, and I've got a baker's dozen!
Grab their meat... for the skag dogs... still seems weird.
Nicely done! Few more skags, and I'll be able to advertise my skag dogs have fifty-percent meat! Drop the ingredients off, and you get paid.

That'll teach that arrogant, spatula-wielding bastard! As soon as people taste my new-and-improved skag dogs, I'll be at the top of the culinary establishment once again! And you get free skag dogs for life! Hope you're hungry.

I USED to be culinary royalty. Then one of my rivals spread a rumor that my skag dogs were full of dead skin and toenails. And yeah, while it's technically true, you—you NEVER reveal a chef's secret recipe under the penalty of DEATH! Anyway, my culinary empire crumbled, and I changed my name. For now...
Hey, that's the Big Succ! Grab it and get succ'ing!
Now go harvest some succulent cacti fruit. Those bad boys taste so goddamn delicious my customers won't care WHAT they're eating! Which is... how I prefer it.
And don't you dare judge me! If serving people toenail clippings and dead skin is wrong, I don't wanna be right.
Now, about the Big Succ—its secondary function is what we call in the biz “splash damage”—you know, like ground slams and grenades. Anyway, that means it'll knock those succulents right off! Try it.
Head's up. Those ain't ordinary skag—those bastards are trained succulent sniffers! Kill 'em!
Ughhhhh. I guess I COULD use those skags in my skag dogs... Seems wrong, but I might as well try it. Grab the skag meat.
